Package: reportabs
Title: Makes Reporting ABS Time Series Data Simpler
Version: 0.0.1.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Hamish", "Gamble", , "hamish.gamble@flinders.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Makes reporting ABS TimeSeries data simpler.  It provides
    convenience functions for plotting labour market indicators, and for
    reporting of changes in indicators over time. Links with the aitidata
    package.
License: CC0
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
